(17257, 'Depacofung 200mg/5ml pwd. for susp. 35 ml', 'ديباكوفونج 200 مجم / 5 مل معلق 35 مل', '', '48', 'Fluconazole', 'Debeiky', 'Susp', 'معلق', '', 'Antifungals.triazoles', '200mg', 'Fluconazole can be administered in the treatment of the following fungal infections[L11043]:
